        "description": "Solver is a commercially licensed, version-controlled CFD code (ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2) with documented release notes and regression test suite. Achieves Gradation 2: documented version control and formal release validation by vendor."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 is used under a commercial license with full vendor-supplied regression testing and release notes. Internal SQA log confirms version pinning and input-file archival for all five operating-point simulations. Required level 1 for MRL 2; achieved level 2 via vendor QMS documentation."
    },
    {
